name: Auton
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en: Autonity is an EVM-based, public blockchain designed as decentralised infrastructure focused on trading arbitrary risk factors.  This public chain uses a novel dual token model (auton and newton) and incorporates both Tendermint and native liquid staking.
